<br>
I retract my previous statements.... because in the end, the only advice I have for her is:  <br>
<br>
&quot;Play whatever you want, play what you feel is fun for you, not what others think. Never choose a character because other people nudged you into that choice.&quot;<br>
<br>
And also.... don't feel guilty about starting over. A lot of people in this forum have done it in this server (re-roll their characters).  If you have to keep restarting characters until you get &quot;the perfect one&quot;..... then do it. Never feel guilty about it.  <br>
<br>
In the end, all that matters is that you feel comfortable with your character.... because we spend so much time in this game that our characters become our real avatars.... they are an extension of ourselves, there is a part of us in these characters, sometimes it's not so obvious. And sometimes it takes trial and error before we find the perfect match. <br>
